                     <note>
                        <p>Delhi Persian 937 a. 
</p>
                        <p>List of contents by an unnamed compiler to the <title key="work_22343">Kīmiyā-yi saʿādat</title> of <persName key="viaf_31996761" role="ant">al-Ghazālī</persName>, with recording the main sections and subsections in serial order, written in nastaʿlīq in a gilt ruled frame. 
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. Datable to the late eighteenth century. 
</p>
                        <p>Flyleaf 1Ar contains prayers and notes. 
</p>
                        <p>Flyleaf 1Bv contains prayers and a deleted note. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22343">Fihrist-i kitāb-i Kīmiyā-yi saʿādat</title>
